config SOC_ADRV906X
    bool "ADI ADRV906X SoC driver support"
    depends on (ARCH_ADRV906X || COMPILE_TEST)
    default ARCH_ADRV906X
    help
        This option enables support for the Analog Devices ADRV906x
        System-on-Chip (SoC) platform designed for advanced cellular
        communications applications.

        Say Y here if you are building a kernel for ADRV906X hardware.
        If unsure, say N.
